data.description: "Your Dream Home Awaits in the Ideal Location! Located just minutes from the tranquil Stillhouse Hollow Lake in the sought-after Amity Estates Subdivision, and zoned for the highly regarded Salado ISD, this Timber Ridge construction home is your ticket to convenience and comfort. Featuring 4 spacious bedrooms and 3 full baths, including a luxurious master suite with ample walk-in closets, a generously sized family room, and a covered patio with a fantastic outdoor kitchen/grill area, this property is the epitome of modern living. What's more, the tax-friendly environment of this area ensures your financial peace of mind. Timber Ridge Homes, a highly desired community within Amity Estates, offers the lifestyle you've been dreaming of. Don't miss out on this opportunity – your perfect home is waiting for you. Act fast!"
